[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":164},["ShallowReactive",2],{"portfolio-built-kindly":3},{"page":4,"next":142},{"id":5,"slug":6,"title":7,"displayTitle":8,"intro":9,"featuredMedia":10,"blocks":33},"MSLQrwVyRGOXOuM1qlTjnw","built-kindly","APEX Experts","Kind by Nature. And by Design.","\u003Cp>\u003Cspan data-metadata=\"&lt;!--(figmeta)eyJmaWxlS2V5IjoiMHNCT0M1enFIcTFUNnZBTDdpUDkybyIsInBhc3RlSUQiOjIxMDc4NzEwMjIsImRhdGFUeXBlIjoic2NlbmUifQo=(/figmeta)--&gt;\">\u003C/span>\u003Cstrong>APEX Experts\u003C/strong> creates thoughtful, tech-forward brands&mdash;starting with our own. A brand that shows how we think, how we work, and why it matters.\u003C/p>",{"id":11,"media":12,"device":32},"SoDSSNhTR9Gc_q0j8v1UpQ",{"id":13,"alt":14,"title":14,"focalPoint":15,"width":17,"height":18,"thumbnail":19,"small":20,"medium":21,"responsiveImage":22,"video":14},"an_HE_uGRcq6rKUK1XER5A",null,{"x":16,"y":16},0.5,2889,1689,"https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1754416502-bk-cs-6.png?auto=format&fit=max&h=600&q=85&w=600","https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1754416502-bk-cs-6.png?auto=format&fit=max&h=1000&q=85&w=1000","https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1754416502-bk-cs-6.png?auto=format&fit=max&h=1500&q=85&w=1500",{"srcSet":23,"webpSrcSet":24,"sizes":25,"src":26,"width":27,"height":28,"aspectRatio":29,"alt":14,"title":14,"base64":30,"bgColor":31},"https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1754416502-bk-cs-6.png?auto=format&dpr=0.25&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440 610w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1754416502-bk-cs-6.png?auto=format&dpr=0.5&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440 1220w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1754416502-bk-cs-6.png?auto=format&dpr=0.75&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440 1830w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1754416502-bk-cs-6.png?auto=format&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440 2440w","","(max-width: 2440px) 100vw, 2440px","https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1754416502-bk-cs-6.png?auto=format&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440",2440,1426,1.7104795737122558,"data:image/png;base64,","#f36f35","laptop",[34,79,130],{"id":35,"type":36,"device":32,"items":37},"EweHAQIASN6EvxyfajC9GA","steps_block",[38,58],{"id":39,"media":40,"title":43,"subtitle":44,"text":45,"list":46,"link":14},"KtqS67jfQNOWI3-rfqDuBg",{"id":13,"alt":14,"title":14,"focalPoint":41,"width":17,"height":18,"thumbnail":19,"small":20,"medium":21,"responsiveImage":42,"video":14},{"x":16,"y":16},{"srcSet":23,"webpSrcSet":24,"sizes":25,"src":26,"width":27,"height":28,"aspectRatio":29,"alt":14,"title":14,"base64":30,"bgColor":31},"Product Snapshot.","What we built and why we built it.","\u003Cp>APEX Experts is a creative technology studio that builds digital products, tools, and experiences for care-focused brands. Our own brand is both our test kitchen and our calling card. It&rsquo;s where we get to practice what we preach: thoughtful design, clean technology, and a little spark of unexpected creativity. Every choice, from the name to the illustrations to the motion, was made the same way we make things for our clients: with intention, collaboration, and a clear idea of the people that will be experiencing our brand.\u003C/p>",[47,50,54],{"id":48,"label":49,"text":7},"BtHGqpMHTEKPWBALda8tVA","Product Name",{"id":51,"label":52,"text":53},"Ct19vcRuT-aV7c6RKnLjog","Launched","January 2025",{"id":55,"label":56,"text":57},"WKiBA713SlWgtHFlEnv-Ig","Type","Creative Technology Studio",{"id":59,"media":60,"title":75,"subtitle":76,"text":77,"list":78,"link":14},"R4gU8Rs3TTKzAZa0UykQUA",{"id":61,"alt":14,"title":14,"focalPoint":62,"width":63,"height":64,"thumbnail":65,"small":66,"medium":67,"responsiveImage":68,"video":14},"NjvwRhIDT1Wl0GYDNou3GQ",{"x":16,"y":16},3207,2245,"https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1754416242-bk-cs-2.png?auto=format&fit=max&h=600&q=85&w=600","https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1754416242-bk-cs-2.png?auto=format&fit=max&h=1000&q=85&w=1000","https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1754416242-bk-cs-2.png?auto=format&fit=max&h=1500&q=85&w=1500",{"srcSet":69,"webpSrcSet":24,"sizes":25,"src":70,"width":27,"height":71,"aspectRatio":72,"alt":14,"title":14,"base64":73,"bgColor":74},"https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1754416242-bk-cs-2.png?auto=format&dpr=0.25&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440 610w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1754416242-bk-cs-2.png?auto=format&dpr=0.5&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440 1220w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1754416242-bk-cs-2.png?auto=format&dpr=0.75&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440 1830w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1754416242-bk-cs-2.png?auto=format&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440 2440w","https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1754416242-bk-cs-2.png?auto=format&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440",1708,1.4285077951002227,"data:image/png;base64,","#beb4bd","The Spark.","A shared vision to make ourselves and our customers smile.","\u003Cp>Two founders. Hundreds of ideas. The challenge? Finding the one name that actually felt like us. We explored names that spoke to our values, our personalities, and the kind of clients we wanted to work with.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>The name APEX Experts clicked. It captured what we wanted to say: we make things well, we make them thoughtfully, and we make them with care for the people on both sides of the screen.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>With the name in place, we shifted to the bigger challenge: how do we bring it to life in a way that feels distinct, creative, and unmistakably ours?\u003C/p>",[],{"id":80,"type":81,"title":82,"subtitle":83,"text1":84,"text2":85,"media":86},"J5cVoHW5Qz-kwI-WeHOLRg","image_grid_block","The Process.","Finding the voice. Building the world. Bringing it to life.","\u003Cp>The name gave us a foundation, but the identity came to life in the style and the story. We wanted something soft enough to feel kind, clever enough to show our creative chops, and just unexpected enough to stand out in the tech space.\u003C/p>","\u003Cp>That led us to an illustrative style with playful scenes that could flex to tell our story in countless ways. We built a whole world around them: characters, devices, and moments that showed how we think about creativity, technology, and kindness.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>As with any project, when it mattered most, we brought in the right partners. A killer illustrator helped us nail the visual language. Animation and tech partners gave the brand motion and personality. Together, we built a brand that could live everywhere: the website, decks, social, and our first industry report, Kindness Is a Competitive Edge.\u003C/p>",[87,102,116],{"id":88,"alt":14,"title":14,"focalPoint":89,"width":90,"height":91,"thumbnail":92,"small":93,"medium":94,"responsiveImage":95,"video":14},"Zs8TNcz5TPCkK0CGLMRDGw",{"x":16,"y":16},5280,2312,"https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1754416359-bk-cs-3.png?auto=format&fit=max&h=600&q=85&w=600","https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1754416359-bk-cs-3.png?auto=format&fit=max&h=1000&q=85&w=1000","https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1754416359-bk-cs-3.png?auto=format&fit=max&h=1500&q=85&w=1500",{"srcSet":96,"webpSrcSet":24,"sizes":25,"src":97,"width":27,"height":98,"aspectRatio":99,"alt":14,"title":14,"base64":100,"bgColor":101},"https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1754416359-bk-cs-3.png?auto=format&dpr=0.25&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440 610w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1754416359-bk-cs-3.png?auto=format&dpr=0.5&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440 1220w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1754416359-bk-cs-3.png?auto=format&dpr=0.75&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440 1830w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1754416359-bk-cs-3.png?auto=format&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440 2440w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1754416359-bk-cs-3.png?auto=format&dpr=1.5&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440 3660w,https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1754416359-bk-cs-3.png?auto=format&dpr=2&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440 4880w","https://www.datocms-assets.com/163973/1754416359-bk-cs-3.png?auto=format&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440",1068,2.2837370242214536,"data:image/jpeg;base64,","#c0bfb8",{"id":103,"alt":14,"title":14,"focalPoint"